# LocalSend Electron App Development Standards

> **Important**: Before starting any task, please read [ARCHITECTURE.md](/ARCHITECTURE.md) in the project root to understand the complete architecture.

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: React 18 + TypeScript
- **Build Tool**: Vite + Electron
- **Styling**: UnoCSS (atomic CSS)
- **Component Format**: Functional components (.tsx)
- **Logging**: electron-log

## Styling Guidelines

Use UnoCSS atomic class names, no traditional CSS files:

```tsx
// ✅ GOOD - Use UnoCSS class names
<div className="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-sidebar-bg rounded-lg">
  <span className="text-lg font-semibold text-black">Title</span>
</div>

// ❌ BAD - Don't use CSS files or inline styles
<div style={{ display: 'flex' }}>
<div className={styles.container}>
```

